## CONSTRAINTS & ASSUMPTIONS

> Read this section before using any data in this document. It defines trust level, known errors, and open questions. Treat ✓ as verified from primary source. Treat ⚠️ as assumption or secondary source only.

| # | Item | Status | Action |
|---|---|---|---|
| C1 | Open API is in **beta** | ⚠️ Unstable surface | Monitor `docs.fourthwall.com` for breaking changes before building |
| C2 | Platform OAuth is **invite-only** | ✓ Primary | Use Basic Auth for all single-shop OIS automation. Do not attempt OAuth self-registration. |
| C3 | API base URL is `https://api.fourthwall.com` | ✓ Corrected | Earlier OIS docs used `https://openapi.fourthwall.com` — that URL is wrong |
| C4 | API path versioning is **inconsistent** | ⚠️ Unresolved | Auth guide shows `/open-api/v1/`, Shop spec shows `/open-api/v1.0/`, Memberships shows `/open-api/v1.1/`. Fetch `llms.txt` and verify each path before implementing |
| C5 | Webhook signature header is `X-Fourthwall-Hmac-SHA256` | ✓ Corrected | Earlier OIS docs stated `X-Fourthwall-Signature` — that is wrong and will silently fail |
| C6 | Webhook delivery is **at-least-once, not exactly-once** | ✓ Primary | Deduplicate on event `id` field. Same event can arrive multiple times. |
| C7 | Webhook ordering is **not guaranteed** | ✓ Primary | `ORDER_UPDATED` may arrive before `ORDER_PLACED`. Build order-agnostic handlers. |
| C8 | Webhook delivery is **not guaranteed** | ✓ Primary | Implement reconciliation polling against Platform API for any data requiring consistency |
| C9 | Content-gating **is supported** | ✓ Corrected | Earlier OIS docs said Fourthwall has no post-gating. Wrong. Memberships API has full per-post access control. See §7. |
| C10 | Credential creation requires **SUPER ADMIN** role | ✓ Primary | Shop owner = SUPER ADMIN by default. Team members cannot create API keys without this role. |
| C11 | `state` param on Posts endpoint is **required** | ✓ Primary | Missing it returns 400. Must pass `Published`, `Scheduled`, or `All`. |
| C12 | Subscription webhook names differ across sources | ⚠️ Alias | Older docs: `SUBSCRIPTION_CREATED/DELETED`. Current API: `SUBSCRIPTION_PURCHASED/EXPIRED`. Treat as equivalent. |
| C13 | Twitch Gifting webhooks are **beta** | ⚠️ Beta | `GIFT_DRAW_STARTED` / `GIFT_DRAW_ENDED` require StreamElements + separate Gifting App setup |
| C14 | Fee and economics data | ⚠️ Secondary | Sourced from FW vs. Patreon analysis (March 2026) — verify at fourthwall.com before financial decisions |
| C15 | Merch product specs | ⚠️ Secondary | Sourced from OIS Artist Export Specs (March 2026) — verify dimensions at help.fourthwall.com before sending to production |

