## 1. OVERVIEW

Fourthwall is a creator commerce and membership platform. Single branded storefront at a custom domain. Acts as **Merchant of Record** — collects and remits sales tax.

```
WHAT IT COVERS    Merch · Memberships · Donations · Digital products · Sales channels
WHAT IT IS NOT    Discovery platform · Per-creation billing · Patreon content-gate equivalent (see C9)
SCALE             200,000+ creators · Stores +48% YoY (as of early 2026)
PRO PLAN          $19/mo — removes 5% fee on digital products only
```

Core commerce flow:
```
Browse → Cart → Checkout (Fourthwall-hosted) → Order completion
```

---

