## 6. NATIVE INTEGRATIONS

No code required. Enable from Fourthwall dashboard.

### 6.1 Discord `✓ Secondary`

```
Setup    Dashboard → Settings → Discord
Maps     Membership tiers → Discord roles
Assigns  On SUBSCRIPTION_PURCHASED
Removes  On SUBSCRIPTION_EXPIRED
Key diff Only manages its own assigned roles — does not strip roles from other bots
Try this BEFORE building a custom Discord bot for role assignment
```

