## 7. MEMBERSHIPS API (Posts) `✓ Primary`

```
Base URL   https://api.fourthwall.com
Prefix     /open-api/v1.1/memberships/
Scope      memberships_read (read) · memberships_write (write)
```

**List posts:**
```
GET /open-api/v1.1/memberships/posts

Required params: state = Published | Scheduled | All  (see C11)
Optional params: page · limit · search_query · types[] · ids[] · tags_ids[]
types[]: Text · Poll · Image · Audio · Video
```

**Access control object (on every post):**
```json
{
  "access": {
    "type": "Public | FreeMembers | FreeAndPaidMembers | MembersOnly | Plans",
    "tiers": [{ "id": 123 }]
  }
}
```

**Post types:** Text · Poll · Image · Audio · Video · VideoEmbed

**VideoEmbed sources:** YouTube · Streamable · Vimeo

**Post statuses:**
```
resources: None | Created | Processing | Completed | Errored
post:      Created | Ready | Live | Finished | Archived
schedule:  None | Asap | Future | Done
```

