## 9. ZAPIER `⚠️ Secondary`

12 triggers · 4 actions. Connects to Notion without custom code.

**Triggers:** New Subscription · Subscription Changed · Subscription Expired · New Order · New Donation · Gift Purchase · Product Created · Product Updated · Newsletter Subscribed · Thank You Sent · Order Updated · Order Placed

**Actions:** Create/Update Product · Update Order · Subscribe to Mailing List · Raw HTTP Request

**OIS flows via Zapier:**
```
New Subscription     → Notion: create row in Members DB
Subscription Changed → Notion: update tier field
Subscription Expired → Notion: update status to lapsed
New Order            → Notion: log to Fulfillment tracker
```

